.DT
get_files_recursive
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
get_files_recursive

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
get_files_recursive -  This method returns all the files (or directories if the dirs flag is 1) in the subdirectories of the specified path.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string * get_files_recursive(string path,
int dirs)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^path%^RESET%^ - the path to get the files for
%^BOLD%^dirs%^RESET%^ - set to 1 to get all subdirs, instead of files

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/path.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns all the files (or directories if the dirs
flag is 1) in the subdirectories of the specified path.
If the dirs flag is set to anything higher than 1, then both
files and directories will be returned.
.EP

